      <title>莫桑比克新任财政部长上任第一天就面临债务问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/mozambique-s-new-finance-chief-faces-debt-headache-from-day-one</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克新任财政部长卡拉·洛韦拉（Carla Louveira）接手的国库因数月的动乱而变得虚弱，而且还要应对潜在的债务重组和政府雇员的罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/mozambique-s-new-finance-chief-faces-debt-headache-from-day-one</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:38:17 GMT</pubDate>
