    <item>
      <title>欧盟将与特朗普政府一起提高对拜登人工智能芯片的限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/eu-to-raise-biden-s-ai-chip-curbs-with-trump-administration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，欧盟将对美国限制英伟达等公司向其部分成员国出口人工智能芯片的决定向美国提出担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/eu-to-raise-biden-s-ai-chip-curbs-with-trump-administration</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:31:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
