    <item>
      <title>中国表示愿意与受制裁的马可·卢比奥对话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/china-signals-willingness-to-speak-with-sanctioned-marco-rubio</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，对美国国务卿卢比奥的制裁不会影响两国官方交流，表明北京方面寻求与特朗普政府就贸易和其他争端进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/china-signals-willingness-to-speak-with-sanctioned-marco-rubio</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 08:56:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塔利班释放美国公民，与被监禁的阿富汗人交换囚犯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/taliban-releases-us-citizens-in-prisoner-swap-for-jailed-afghan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿富汗塔利班政府周二宣布，已释放美国公民，以交换被关押在美国监狱的一名阿富汗囚犯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/taliban-releases-us-citizens-in-prisoner-swap-for-jailed-afghan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 06:25:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾总理称预算调整削弱台湾国防实力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/taiwan-premier-says-opposition-s-budget-moves-would-hurt-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾行政院长赵荣泰表示，反对派议员今年对部分军事资金（包括备受瞩目的潜艇项目）附加条件的举动将破坏台湾的防御能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/taiwan-premier-says-opposition-s-budget-moves-would-hurt-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 06:12:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平避开特朗普早期的关税，为中国争取时间影响美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/xi-dodges-early-trump-tariffs-buying-china-time-to-influence-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于国家主席习近平来说，唐纳德·特朗普的总统任期开局本来会很火爆，此前他在竞选时曾承诺要用关税惩罚中国。然而，这位美国领导人上任第一天就为北京赢得了意想不到的喘息空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/xi-dodges-early-trump-tariffs-buying-china-time-to-influence-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 05:41:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯警告投资者不会相信未来的支出削减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/reeves-warned-investors-won-t-believe-in-future-spending-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 宣布进一步推迟支出限制，她将很难让金融城相信她的财政信誉，因为她已经试图将有政治争议的决定推迟到工党议会任期的结束阶段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/reeves-warned-investors-won-t-believe-in-future-spending-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统尹永康否认在弹劾审判中存在不当行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/south-korea-s-arrested-president-to-appear-at-impeachment-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈首次出席弹劾审判，该审判调查了他上个月令人震惊的短暂戒严令，他否认自己有任何不当行为，并称自己是民主的坚定信徒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/south-korea-s-arrested-president-to-appear-at-impeachment-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 01:52:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划在 2 月 1 日前对墨西哥、加拿大征收 25% 关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-plans-to-enact-25-tariffs-on-mexico-canada-by-feb-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他计划在 2 月 1 日之前对墨西哥和加拿大征收高达 25% 的关税，重申了他的观点，即美国的两个邻国正在让无证移民和毒品涌入该国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-plans-to-enact-25-tariffs-on-mexico-canada-by-feb-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 00:57:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
